@Chandra.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5140
@ApiKey = dev-api-key-change-me

### Health
GET {{Chandra.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

### OCR – base64 JSON body
POST {{Chandra.Api_HostAddress}}/api/ocr/base64
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fileName": "sample.pdf",
  "fileBase64": "<base64-encoded file>",
  "format": "markdown",
  "pageRange": "1-3",
  "includeHeadersFooters": false
}

###
